---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layouts.astro';
---

<Layout title="Experience - Karthik Menon">
	<section class="py-24 px-6">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Work Experience</h1>
			<p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-16">Professional journey bridging HR strategy, data analytics, and organizational health.</p>
			
			<div class="space-y-12">
				<!-- JD.com Experience -->
				<div class="border-l-2 border-blue-500 pl-8 pb-12">
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950"></div>
						
						<div class="mb-2">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">HRBP (Project Contract - Intern)</h2>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 items-center text-slate-400 mt-2">
								<span class="font-semibold text-blue-400">JD.com (Benelux)</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span>Rotterdam, Netherlands</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span class="text-sm">Sep 2025 - Oct 2025</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								Acted as functional lead for Hire-to-Pay analytics, partnering with global stakeholders to translate business questions into technical reporting requirements while establishing data integrity standards.
							</p>
							
							<div class="space-y-3 text-slate-400">
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Reporting Strategy & Requirements:</span> Acted as the functional lead for Hire-to-Pay analytics. Partnered with global stakeholders to translate vague business questions into strict technical reporting requirements.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Data Product Design:</span> Audited and redesigned the metric taxonomy for headcount reporting, establishing a single source of truth across Finance and HR datasets to ensure data integrity.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Stakeholder Management:</span> Collaborated with cross-functional leadership to validate data accuracy for new reports, ensuring alignment on definitions and methodology before deployment.</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-6">
								<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 mb-3">Key Technologies & Skills</h3>
								<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">People Analytics</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Metric Taxonomy Design</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Data Integrity</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Stakeholder Management</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Requirements Gathering</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Cummins Experience -->
				<div class="border-l-2 border-blue-500 pl-8 pb-12">
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950"></div>
						
						<div class="mb-2">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">HR Strategy Intern - Process Optimization</h2>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 items-center text-slate-400 mt-2">
								<span class="font-semibold text-blue-400">Cummins Emission Solutions</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span>Roermond, Netherlands</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span class="text-sm">Feb 2025 - Jul 2025</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								Designed and deployed custom analytics solutions to optimize workforce capacity planning, while establishing automated workflows that reduced manual reporting effort by 45%.
							</p>
							
							<div class="space-y-3 text-slate-400">
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Dashboard Development:</span> Designed and deployed a custom Power BI dashboard to track operational capacity and training flexibility, directly supporting the forward capacity planning process.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Process Automation:</span> Identified manual reporting bottlenecks and built automated data workflows (Python/Power Automate) that reduced reporting effort by 45%, allowing for more frequent scenario planning.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Insight Generation:</span> Partnered with 7 department heads to interpret capacity data, providing actionable recommendations that optimized shift scheduling and headcount allocation.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Governance:</span> Spearheaded GDPR alignment to ensure all workforce data handling met global compliance standards.</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-6">
								<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 mb-3">Key Technologies & Skills</h3>
								<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Power BI</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Python</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Power Automate</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">GDPR Compliance</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Capacity Planning</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Process Optimization</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Café de Opstand Experience -->
				<div class="border-l-2 border-blue-500 pl-8 pb-12">
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] w-6 h-6 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950"></div>
						
						<div class="mb-2">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Organizational Change Analyst</h2>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 items-center text-slate-400 mt-2">
								<span class="font-semibold text-blue-400">Café de Opstand</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span>Nijmegen, Netherlands</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span class="text-sm">Oct 2024 - Dec 2024</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								Owned end-to-end delivery of retention analysis, conducting Root Cause Analysis on volunteer attrition data to inform future resourcing strategies. Delivered strategic recommendations that increased short-term retention by 40%.
							</p>
							
							<div class="space-y-3 text-slate-400">
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Ad Hoc Analysis:</span> Owned the end-to-end delivery of retention analysis, conducting Root Cause Analysis (RCA) on volunteer attrition data to inform future resourcing strategies.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p><span class="font-semibold text-slate-300">Impact:</span> Delivered a strategic recommendation package that increased short-term retention by 40%, demonstrating the ability to synthesize analysis and prioritize next steps.</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-6">
								<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 mb-3">Key Skills</h3>
								<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Root Cause Analysis</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Retention Analytics</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Strategic Recommendations</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Change Management</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Previous Experience Placeholder -->
				<div class="border-l-2 border-slate-700 pl-8 pb-12">
					<div class="relative">
						<div class="absolute -left-[41px] w-6 h-6 bg-slate-700 rounded-full border-4 border-slate-950"></div>
						
						<div class="mb-2">
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Entrepreneurial Ventures</h2>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 items-center text-slate-400 mt-2">
								<span class="font-semibold">Small-Scale Business Management</span>
								<span>•</span>
								<span class="text-sm">Prior Experience</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
							<p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
								Built and managed small-scale ventures, developing an "owner mindset" and ability to assess market needs quickly while optimizing resources for maximum impact.
							</p>
							
							<div class="space-y-3 text-slate-400">
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p>Rapid market assessment and strategic positioning</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p>Resource optimization and operational efficiency</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex gap-3">
									<span class="text-blue-400 mt-1">•</span>
									<p>End-to-end business management and stakeholder engagement</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-6">
								<h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 mb-3">Key Skills Developed</h3>
								<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Strategic Thinking</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Adaptability</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Problem Solving</span>
									<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded-full text-xs text-slate-300">Owner Mindset</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Call to Action -->
			<div class="mt-16 bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Interested in my experience?</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">Let's discuss how my background can add value to your organization.</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
					<a href="/contact" class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors">
						Contact Me
					</a>
					<a href="/resume.pdf" download class="px-6 py-3 border border-slate-600 hover:border-slate-500 text-slate-300 hover:text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors">
						Download CV
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
